A nuclear Saturday?

88
00:06:44,153 --> 00:06:45,570
Come on, guys.

89
00:06:45,780 --> 00:06:47,906
This is our last weekend together.

90
00:06:48,116 --> 00:06:49,866
Last Goonie weekend.

91
00:06:50,368 --> 00:06:52,577
