94
00:06:59,961 --> 00:07:03,171
The one older brother had to go
and screw it up.

95
00:07:05,007 --> 00:07:08,760
Flunking your driver's test?
I don't know what to do with you.

96
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:11,096
You guys, let me in!

97
00:07:11,305 --> 00:07:12,431
